4515,Tostitos® Chips,Tostitos® Bite Size Rounds Tortilla Chips,https://www.tostitos.ca/products/tostitos®-bite-size-rounds-tortilla-chips,rounds-bite-size.png,Rounds,"

Try this. Grab a Bite Size Round, dip it into some Tostitos® salsa, and pop into your mouth. Fits perfectly. They're just like Tostitos® Restaurant Style tortilla chips, only smaller and round. Made from premium white corn, Tostitos® Bite Size Rounds tortilla chips, are a versatile snack. Each chip delivers a hearty crunch and a light burst of flavour, topped off with a touch of salt. Serve up your Tostitos®; tortilla chips with a savoury Tostitos® salsa for a crowd-pleasing snack experience.

","Corn, vegetable oil, salt, calcium hydroxide.",,Amount per 50 g serving (40 chips),"- Calories
No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Preservatives

Tortilla chips with a dash of jalapeño!

Add a bag of Tostitos®Hint of Jalapeño flavoured tortilla chips to any social gathering or party for an instant hit! 

These crispy, premium white corn tortilla chips are lightly seasoned with a touch of spice in every bite for the perfect, authentic flavour experience. Enjoy on their own, or pair with your favourite queso and salsas for even more flavour!

Tortilla chips with a twist of lime! Add a bag of Tostitos® Hint of Lime flavoured Tortilla Chips to any social gathering or party for a zesty treat. These crispy, premium white corn tortilla chips have a splash of lime taste in every bite for an extra bit of zing. Perfect for dipping, perfect for sharing - just perfect any time.

Tostitos® Multigrain Rounds tortilla chips are made with the goodness of four grains: corn, buckwheat flour, whole oat flour and whole wheat flour. Pour a bag of Tostitos® Multigrain Rounds tortilla chips, with your favourite Tostitos® salsa, or serve them up as nachos and watch your guests make them disappear.

What came first, the chip or the bowl? Either way, Tostitos® Multigrain Scoops!® tortilla chips combines them both perfectly! With every light tasting bite, there's a whole lot of wholegrain goodness from corn, buckwheat flour, whole oat flour and whole wheat flour! Serve these multigrain tortilla chips at your next gathering. Whether it’s family Mexican food night or a game night with friends, there are plenty of Tostitos® Multigrain Scoops!® chips to go around!

For all the garlic lovers, this Tostitos® salsa includes lots of deliciously roasted garlic in addition to vine harvested tomatoes, onions and jalapeño peppers. Enjoy it with Tostitos® tortilla chips or use it as a topper for your meat, fish or eggs! Bring out the dip and break out the fun by placing several bowls of Tostitos® Roasted Garlic Salsa dip around the room at your next party.

,0,1,triangles-garlic-blackbean.png 4527,Salsa and Dips,Tostitos® Roasted Red Pepper Salsa,https://www.tostitos.ca/products/tostitos®-roasted-red-pepper-salsa,Salsa-Roasted-Red_0.png,Salsa,

Tostitos® Roasted Red Pepper Salsa is your favourite salsa with the delicious addition of grilled red peppers making it a perfect complement for any Tostitos® tortilla chip! Its chunky thickness helps it stay on the chip for a savoury burst of bold taste with each bite. Pour the salsa in a bowl and serve it alongside tortilla chips, or set it out as an optional topping for Mexican dishes. While there's enough salsa in this jar to serve a large party, you can also enjoy it on your own. Just be sure to refrigerate the salsa after opening. The packaging makes for easy transportation to and from parties — just open, pour, serve and enjoy.

","Tomato puree (water, tomato paste), diced tomatoes in tomato juice (contains calcium chloride, citric acid), roasted red peppers, onions, water, jalapeño peppers, salt, vinegar, flavour (contains carrot juice, onion broth, onion powder, autolyzed yeast), garlic powder.
